      "writtenOn": "2016-02-27T02:03:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Got it, that would be nice, but: I asked Prathmesh, and he says we can\u0027t count on the backend processing separate requests properly. I suppose I will just check the length of the resulting URL, and then remove keys if it doesn\u0027t fit (starting with GPU info).",
      "parentUuid": "e2b0b90b_569888a3",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 73,
        "startChar": 20,
